      • Prescription

        public Prescription(int id,
                    User recipient,
                    java.time.LocalDate issueDate,
                    ApprovedStages approvedStage,
                    UsedStages usedStage,
                    Medicine prescribedMedication)
        Class constructor specifying prescription id, recipient object of this prescription, date of receipt of the recipe, recipe approval stage, recipe used stage and medicine object for which a prescription is issued.
        Parameters:
        id - prescription number in integer format
        recipient - the recipient's object on whose face the prescription is written.
        issueDate - date of receipt of the recipe
        approvedStage - recipe approval stage
        usedStage - recipe used stage
        prescribedMedication - medicine object for which a prescription is issued
